<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Terms of Service - Akhfhid Bot</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/variables.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/base.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/layout.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/components.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/pages.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        .legal-content {
            background: var(--bg-card);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            margin-top: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        .legal-content h1 {
            color: var(--text-primary);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        .legal-content h2 {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .legal-content p, .legal-content ul {
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .legal-content ul {
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            color: var(--text-secondary);
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <%- include('partials/sidebar') %>
        
        <div class="right-panel">
            <div class="content-area">
                <a href="/" class="back-link"><i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Back to Dashboard</a>
                
                <div class="legal-content">
                    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
                    <p>Last updated: November 2025</p>

                    <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
                    <p>By inviting or using Akhfhid Bot, you agree to these Terms of Service.</p>

                    <h2>2. Usage Rules</h2>
                    <p>You agree not to use the bot for:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Spamming commands or abusing the bot's resources.</li>
                        <li>Violating Discord's Terms of Service or Community Guidelines.</li>
                        <li>Any illegal activities.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>3. Availability</h2>
                    <p>We strive to keep the bot online 24/7, but we do not guarantee uninterrupted service. Maintenance may occur at any time.</p>

                    <h2>4. Termination</h2>
                    <p>We reserve the right to block any user or server from using the bot if they violate these terms.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
